data.description: Nestled within the heart of historic Lincolnton, a home of unparalleled charm and sophistication awaits its next chapter. Welcome to 519 Madison Street, where history and modernity intertwine seamlessly, inviting you to embark on a journey through a residence that encapsulates the essence of Southern living. The main level features a huge open floor plan that includes the kitchen, family room, dining room, a sitting area, a office and a hallway leading to the stairs.  Up stairs you will find 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  The entire home has been updated electrical, plumbing, new footings in front corners of home, new HVAC (2022) new insulation in attic, refinished original hard wood floors, new plank flooring in kitchen/living room, new kitchen appliances, granite countertops, tile on fireplace, all new doors inside and out, new carpet upstairs, fully enclosed new fencing in back yard, and a new samsung smart refrigerator.  This home is a must see.
